---
---
<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <p class="section-label">About</p>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <h2 class="about-heading">
        Design at the<br />
        <span class="light">intersection</span><br />
        of craft & code.
      </h2>
      <div class="about-body">
        <p>
          I'm Adam — a UI/UX Designer based in the Philippines with over 8 years
          of experience turning complex problems into elegant, intuitive digital
          experiences.
        </p>
        <p>
          My background spans fintech, insurance, marketplaces, and Web3 —
          giving me a rare ability to design for highly regulated, data-rich
          environments without sacrificing beauty or usability.
        </p>
        <p>
          I care deeply about the full picture: from user research and flows to
          pixel-perfect UI and scalable design systems. With a foundation in
          software development, I bridge design and engineering naturally.
        </p>
        <div class="expertise">
          <div class="expertise-col">
            <p class="expertise-label">Expertise</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Product Design</li>
              <li>UX Research</li>
              <li>Design Systems</li>
              <li>Brand Identity</li>
              <li>Motion Design</li>
              <li>Prototyping</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="expertise-col">
            <p class="expertise-label">Industries</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Web3 / Blockchain</li>
              <li>Fintech</li>
              <li>Payments</li>
              <li>EdTech</li>
              <li>E-commerce</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="expertise-col">
            <p class="expertise-label">Tools</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Figma</li>
              <li>After Effects</li>
              <li>Jira / Notion</li>
              <li>Claude</li>
              <li>Cursor</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 8rem var(--pad);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4.5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    position: sticky;
    top: 8rem;
  }

  .about-heading .light {
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-body p {
    font-size: clamp(0.92rem, 1.4vw, 1rem);
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .expertise {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .expertise-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }

  .expertise ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .expertise li {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .about-heading { position: static; }
    .expertise { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .expertise { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
